},{"pid":"6d4b572d8be17211cb75fcdde28eddd3e85c74ce","tid":533390,"uid":142466,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T18:32:32.000Z","msg":"藥膏布味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a7b7fb9acc5ab4267d77fec821ee7913e5c6e4a","tid":533390,"uid":92467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T18:41:59.000Z","msg":"正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"567efc135e45e087466032b1819d13d9017701f3","tid":533390,"uid":25329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T18:50:37.000Z","msg":"細個時覺得好撚難飲 大個咗就幾鍾意"},{"pid":"aa8f339216133fb6a39ca53e12d528f7b545be41","tid":533390,"uid":21462,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T18:53:09.000Z","msg":"由細到大都好中意飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3b8efaab5a6e8e0473a38d31612057881b9911a","tid":533390,"uid":63588,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T18:56:45.000Z","msg":"屎水來"},{"pid":"ce9eb1394c28ca1d7af2f2dd67ecf4c14fbdcfb2","tid":533390,"uid":122624,"like":58,"dislike":1,"score":57,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T19:21:59.000Z","msg":"細個果陣阿媽會買定啲可樂同檸檬茶果啲放係雪櫃<br />\n但係成日都比我地啲細路飲哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢想拎黎飲果陣就會無哂 或者得返一兩包係度<br />\n<br />\n因為經常發生呢個問題<br />\n跟住我阿媽就試下每款汽水都買啲<br />\n睇下我地有咩汽水係唔飲既<br />\n比佢發現左我地幾兄弟姊妹都唔鐘意飲沙示<br />\n<br />\n自此之後屋企個雪櫃就無出現過其他汽水<br />\n只係得返沙示呢隻藥水味既汽水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢個情況維持左幾個月 <br />\n阿媽都開心左幾個月 有時佢放工返到屋企 <br />\n攤係梳化一路睇電視一路嘆住罐沙示 <br />\n同我地講(沙示先最好飲呀 你地就唔識欣賞啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n直到有一日我硬住頭皮去克服呢隻味<br />\n跟住再去荼毒啲阿哥家姐<br />\n結果我地又成功清哂雪櫃啲野飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而家人大左有時都會買返罐沙示黎飲下<br />\n有時覺得沙示先係真正既汽水<br />\n因為堅係勁有汽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55c0f2751c419ca0327595796fa870518fe631e0","tid":533390,"uid":152244,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T19:47:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>細個果陣阿媽會買定啲可樂同檸檬茶果啲放係雪櫃<br />\n但係成日都比我地啲細路飲哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢想拎黎飲果陣就會無哂 或者得返一兩包係度<br />\n<br />\n因為經常發生呢個問題<br />\n跟住我阿媽就試下每款汽水都買啲<br />\n睇下我地有咩汽水係唔飲既<br />\n比佢發現左我地幾兄弟姊妹都唔鐘意飲沙示<br />\n<br />\n自此之後屋企個雪櫃就無出現過其他汽水<br />\n只係得返沙示呢隻藥水味既汽水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢個情況維持左幾個月 <br />\n阿媽都開心左幾個月 有時佢放工返到屋企 <br />\n攤係梳化一路睇電視一路嘆住罐沙示 <br />\n同我地講(沙示先最好飲呀 你地就唔識欣賞啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n直到有一日我硬住頭皮去克服呢隻味<br />\n跟住再去荼毒啲阿哥家姐<br />\n結果我地又成功清哂雪櫃啲野飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而家人大左有時都會買返罐沙示黎飲下<br />\n有時覺得沙示先係真正既汽水<br />\n因為堅係勁有汽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可以拍成廣告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5729d93b7aa5c63dea403f8f474fb863145a853e","tid":533390,"uid":123251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T19:50:50.000Z","msg":"Root beer正啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fbf257fdebeb005d0cb002eb7049688ae77ca80","tid":533390,"uid":33077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T02:42:05.000Z","msg":"由細到大都鐘意飲"},{"pid":"8abfff928337c0caaa08609698487af9c890409d","tid":533390,"uid":39628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4fbf257fdebeb005d0cb002eb7049688ae77ca80","tid":533390,"uid":33077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T02:42:05.000Z","msg":"由細到大都鐘意飲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T03:41:46.000Z","msg":"x2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe01f97a4e8bd36c53a64c3155ee501ce2269e65","